description: Taking her culinary background and experience, as well as her passion for food, Aunt Shirley is now shaking things up on the streets of Dallas with her tasty fried chicken dishes and signature sweet potato creations. A few of the incredibly scrumptious items you’ll find on her menu include waffles (with flavors like sweet potato, red velvet, bacon, and Belgian), paired perfectly with juicy fried chicken (with flavors like buffalo, lemon pepper, garlic parmesan, hickory smoked BBQ, and home style). There are also fries which you can customize with more fun flavors, a wide variety of wonderful waffle toppings, sweet potato brownies, blended frappes, and so much more. The list of deliciousness just goes on and on. For a taste of something real great, you’ll surely want to come on out to Aunt Shirley’s Food Truck.
name: Aunt Shirley's Food Truck
